---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="TRT Evaluation" description="Lab-driven testosterone evaluation with honest, clinical assessment. Not a sales-driven TRT clinic. Telehealth across Florida.">

  <section class="pt-40 pb-28 sm:pt-48 sm:pb-36">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal max-w-3xl">
        <span class="label text-primary block mb-5">TRT Evaluation</span>
        <h1 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(3rem,7vw,5.5rem)] leading-[1.0] tracking-[-0.03em] text-text mb-8">
          Lab-driven testosterone<br /><em class="text-primary italic">evaluation</em> and care
        </h1>
        <p class="text-text/50 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-[540px] mb-10">
          A comprehensive, evaluation-first approach. We start with symptoms and labs — not a sales pitch. If TRT isn't right for you, we'll tell you.
        </p>
        <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center font-ui text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] bg-primary text-bg border border-primary px-7 py-3 rounded-[4px] hover:bg-accent hover:border-accent transition-all duration-300">Book a Visit</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Steps -->
  <section class="pb-28 sm:pb-36">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <span class="label text-primary block mb-5">Our Process</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text">Evaluation before <em class="text-primary italic">everything</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Symptom Evaluation</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text/50 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Structured review of fatigue, mood, libido, concentration</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Full medical history and medications assessment</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Open discussion before any decisions</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Lab-Based Assessment</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text/50 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Testosterone panel: total, free testosterone, SHBG</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Comprehensive bloodwork including CBC</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Provider-led results review with clear explanation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 border border-border rounded-2xl p-8">
          <h3 class="font-display font-light text-2xl text-text mb-4">Monitoring & Adjustments</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-text/50 text-sm">
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Regular follow-up check-ins if TRT is appropriate</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Individualized dose adjustments based on labs</li>
            <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-primary mt-0.5">&#8226;</span> Periodic monitoring labs every 3–6 months</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Philosophy -->
  <section class="py-28 sm:py-36 border-t border-border">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text mb-8">
          Honest evaluation,<br />not a <em class="text-accent italic">sales funnel</em>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-text/40 text-base leading-relaxed mb-12 max-w-[540px] mx-auto">
          Unlike many TRT clinics, we don't start with the assumption that you need testosterone. We start with your symptoms and your labs. If TRT isn't clinically appropriate, we'll be upfront about it.
        </p>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">
          <div class="border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
            <span class="font-display font-light text-3xl text-primary block mb-3">Labs first</span>
            <p class="text-text/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Decisions driven by your bloodwork, not assumptions.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
            <span class="font-display font-light text-3xl text-primary block mb-3">Honest talk</span>
            <p class="text-text/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">We'll tell you if TRT isn't the right fit.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border border-border rounded-xl p-6">
            <span class="font-display font-light text-3xl text-primary block mb-3">Ongoing care</span>
            <p class="text-text/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Not a one-visit clinic. We monitor and adjust.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="py-28 sm:py-36 border-t border-border">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal mb-16">
        <span class="label text-primary block mb-5">Common Questions</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text">What to <em class="text-primary italic">know</em></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="max-w-3xl space-y-4">
        {[
          { q: 'Can TRT be managed via telehealth?', a: 'Yes. Symptom evaluation, lab ordering, results review, and ongoing management can all be handled effectively through telehealth visits.' },
          { q: 'Do you accept insurance for TRT?', a: 'No. MBS Medical is a cash-pay practice. This keeps your care simple, private, and free from insurance-driven limitations.' },
          { q: 'What if I\'m not a candidate for TRT?', a: 'We\'ll be upfront about it. If your labs and symptoms don\'t support TRT, your provider will explain why and discuss alternative approaches.' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <details class="reveal group border border-border rounded-xl">
            <summary class="flex items-center justify-between px-6 py-5 cursor-pointer text-text font-display font-light text-xl">
              {item.q}
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-text-muted group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform shrink-0 ml-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
            </summary>
            <div class="px-6 pb-5 text-text/50 text-base leading-relaxed">{item.a}</div>
          </details>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-28 sm:py-36 border-t border-border">
    <div class="max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 sm:px-8 lg:px-12">
      <div class="reveal grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-20 items-center">
        <div class="border-l-[3px] border-primary pl-8 sm:pl-10">
          <h2 class="font-display font-light text-[clamp(2.5rem,5vw,4rem)] leading-[1.1] text-text">Start with an <em class="text-primary italic">evaluation</em></h2>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-text/50 text-base leading-relaxed mb-8 max-w-[480px]">Get a clear, lab-based picture of where you stand — no pressure, no sales pitch.</p>
          <a href="https://mbsmedical.practicebetter.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center font-ui text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.15em] bg-primary text-bg border border-primary px-7 py-3 rounded-[4px] hover:bg-accent hover:border-accent transition-all duration-300">Book a Visit</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
<script>
  const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => { entries.forEach((e) => { if (e.isIntersecting) e.target.classList.add('visible'); }); }, { threshold: 0.08, rootMargin: '0px 0px -40px 0px' });
  document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
</script>
